Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time for SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to be followed by Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to transition to SW-Checklist Completed compared to the time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that end with SW-EIC Reject versus those that proceed to reviewer assignment (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Reject occurs

Name: Time until SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion is succeeded by any checklist-related reminder activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days or SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion from the start of the process in variants where it appears after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation versus before it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed in end-to-end variants that reach reviewer agreement
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants that successfully assign reviewers, excluding cases that terminate early (e.g., Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion cycle in comparison with the cycle time of SW-Initial Reviewer Selection within the same case trajectories
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-EIC Accept in successful publication paths
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to be completed before any plagiarism-related activity (e.g., Plagiarism Originality Report Completed or Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded) occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
